#: .\armor.json
msgid "faraday plate suit"
msgid_plural "faraday plate suits"
msgstr[0] "法拉第板甲套装"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'faraday plate suit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A suit of Gothic plate armor, complete with gloves, gauntlets, and a barbute"
" helmet.  It has been conductively interconnected, protecting against "
"electricity."
msgstr "一套哥特式板甲，包括手套、护手和带面罩头盔。已进行导电互连，可抵御电击。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "皮革连体服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather.  Provides decent storage "
"and proteciton, and is not very encumbering."
msgstr "一件由厚皮革制成的短袖连体服。提供不错的存储空间和防护，且不十分累赘。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "armored leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "armored leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "装甲皮革连体服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'armored leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"An armored short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather and metal plates."
"  Cumbersome, but offers excellent protection from harm."
msgstr "一件由厚皮革和金属板制成的装甲短袖连体服。笨重，但提供极佳的伤害防护。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "tire armor"
msgid_plural "tire armors"
msgstr[0] "轮胎护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tire armor'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"Makeshift armor made from parts of cut up tires.  Incredibly thick and tough"
" but just as encumbering."
msgstr "由切割轮胎部件制成的临时护甲。极其厚重坚固，但同样累赘。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "hard chest protector"
msgid_plural "hard chest protectors"
msgstr[0] "硬质护胸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hard chest protector'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid "A polyurethane chest protector with neoprene backing."
msgstr "一件带氯丁橡胶背衬的聚氨酯护胸。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "conductive suit"
msgid_plural "conductive suits"
msgstr[0] "导电服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'conductive suit'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A one piece conductive suit used in linework.  Provides decent physical "
"protection and full protection against electricity.  The hood is designed to"
" fit over a hardhat."
msgstr "一件用于线路作业的一体式导电服。提供良好的物理防护和全面的电击防护。兜帽设计用于套在安全帽上。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "floating backpack"
msgid_plural "floating backpacks"
msgstr[0] "悬浮背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'floating backpack'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A small backpack with a special rail system designed to reduce the load felt"
" by the wearer when moving up and down.  Good storage for very little "
"encumbrance."
msgstr "一个小型背包，配有特殊轨道系统，旨在减少穿戴者上下移动时的负重感。以极低的累赘度提供良好的存储空间。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "floating rucksack"
msgid_plural "floating rucksacks"
msgstr[0] "悬浮帆布背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'floating rucksack'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A huge military rucksack with a special rail system designed to reduce the "
"load felt by the wearer when moving up and down, provides a lot of storage "
"for moderate encumbrance."
msgstr "一个巨大的军用帆布背包，配有特殊轨道系统，旨在减少穿戴者上下移动时的负重感，以中等累赘度提供大量存储空间。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "XL leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "XL皮革连体服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather.  Provides decent storage "
"and proteciton, and is not very encumbering.  This can be worn regardless of"
" your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件由厚皮革制成的短袖连体服。提供不错的存储空间和防护，且不十分累赘。无论你的突变状态如何，均可穿着。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL armored leather jumpsuit"
msgid_plural "XL armored leather jumpsuits"
msgstr[0] "XL装甲皮革连体服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL armored leather jumpsuit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"An armored short-sleeved jumpsuit made from thick leather and metal plates."
"  Cumbersome, but offers excellent protection from harm.  This can be worn "
"regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件由厚皮革和金属板制成的装甲短袖连体服。笨重，但提供极佳的伤害防护。无论你的突变状态如何，均可穿着。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号皮革护臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL leather arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A pair of massive tough leather arm guards.  Fairly light and comfortable."
msgstr "一副巨大而坚韧的皮革护臂。相当轻便舒适。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather armor gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather armor gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号皮革护手甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather armor gauntlets', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL leather armor gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Heavy and massive fingerless leather gloves.  Very flexible and comfortable."
msgstr "厚重巨大的无指皮革手套。非常灵活舒适。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather gloves"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号皮革手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather gloves', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. XL leather gloves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of black leather gloves."
msgstr "一副巨大的黑色皮革手套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather armor helmet"
msgid_plural "XL leather armor helmets"
msgstr[0] "XL号皮革头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather armor helmet'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive and thick leather helmet that provides excellent protection for "
"the head."
msgstr "一顶巨大厚实的皮革头盔，为头部提供极佳保护。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL scrap suit"
msgid_plural "XL scrap suits"
msgstr[0] "XL号废料护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL scrap suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive suit of armor made from scraps of metal secured by simple strings;"
" provides decent protection, but the loose collection of plates doesn't make"
" for the most convenient protection."
msgstr "一套由简单绳索固定的金属碎片制成的巨大护甲；提供不错的防护，但松散的板甲组合并不便于行动。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL metal arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL metal arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号金属护臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL metal arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL metal arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive pair of arm guards hammered out from metal.  Perfect for the Post-"
"Apocalyptic Warrior look."
msgstr "一副由金属锻造的巨大护臂。完美契合后末日战士风格。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL iron greaves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL iron greaves"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号铁质护胫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL iron greaves', 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL
#. iron greaves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of iron leg guards with a simple leather lining."
msgstr "一副带有简易皮革衬里的巨大铁质腿部护甲。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chitinous gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chitinous gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号几丁质护手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chitinous gauntlets', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL chitinous gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive gauntlets made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Very light and "
"durable."
msgstr "由昆虫外骨骼制成的巨大护手。非常轻便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号生物硅化几丁质护手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets',
#. 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL biosilicified chitin gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive gauntlets crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned "
"biosilicified exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "由精心清洁修剪的酸性蚂蚁生物硅化外骨骼制成的巨大护手。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chitinous helmet"
msgid_plural "XL chitinous helmets"
msgstr[0] "XL号几丁质头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chitinous helmet'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive helmet made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Covers the entire "
"head; very light and durable."
msgstr "一顶由昆虫外骨骼制成的巨大头盔。覆盖整个头部；非常轻便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL biosilicified chitin helmet"
msgid_plural "XL biosilicified chitin helmets"
msgstr[0] "XL号生物硅化几丁质头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL biosilicified chitin helmet'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive helmet crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned biosilicified"
" exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Covers the entire head; acid-resistant and "
"very durable."
msgstr "一顶由精心清洁修剪的酸性蚂蚁生物硅化外骨骼制成的巨大头盔。覆盖整个头部；耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chitin arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chitin arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号几丁质护臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chitin arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL chitin arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A pair of massive arm guards made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Light "
"and durable."
msgstr "一副由昆虫外骨骼制成的巨大护臂。轻便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号生物硅化几丁质护臂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards',
#. 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL biosilicified chitin arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A pair of massive arm guards crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned "
"biosilicified exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "一副由精心清洁修剪的酸性蚂蚁生物硅化外骨骼制成的巨大护臂。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chitinous armor"
msgid_plural "XL chitinous armors"
msgstr[0] "XL号几丁质护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chitinous armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive leg and body armor made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Light and"
" durable."
msgstr "由昆虫外骨骼制成的巨大腿部和躯干护甲。轻便耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL biosilicified chitin armor"
msgid_plural "XL biosilicified chitin armors"
msgstr[0] "XL号生物硅化几丁质护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL biosilicified chitin armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive leg and body armor crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned "
"biosilicified exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "由精心清洁修剪的酸性蚂蚁生物硅化外骨骼制成的巨大腿部和躯干护甲。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL flame-resistant gloves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL flame-resistant gloves"
msgstr[0] "一双XL号阻燃手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL flame-resistant gloves', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL flame-resistant gloves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug fitting pair of gloves made from thin and lightweight Nomex "
"fire-resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, they are light and comfortable"
" to wear under clothing."
msgstr "一副由轻薄诺梅克斯阻燃面料制成的大号紧贴合手套。坚韧且透气，轻便舒适，适合穿在衣物内层。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL flame-resistant hood"
msgid_plural "XL flame-resistant hoods"
msgstr[0] "XL号阻燃头罩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL flame-resistant hood'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug fitting garment that protects your head and neck, made from "
"lightweight Nomex fire-resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, it is light "
"and comfortable to wear under clothing."
msgstr "一件由轻质诺梅克斯阻燃面料制成的大号紧贴合服装，可保护头部和颈部。坚韧且透气，轻便舒适，适合穿在衣物内层。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL flame-resistant socks"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL flame-resistant socks"
msgstr[0] "一双XL号阻燃袜子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL flame-resistant socks', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL flame-resistant socks'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug fitting pair of stockings made from thin and lightweight "
"Nomex fire-resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, they are light and "
"comfortable to wear under clothing."
msgstr "一双由轻薄诺梅克斯阻燃面料制成的大号紧贴合长袜。坚韧且透气，轻便舒适，适合穿在衣物内层。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "flame-resistant suit"
msgid_plural "flame-resistant suits"
msgstr[0] "阻燃套装"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flame-resistant suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, snug body suit made from thin and lightweight Nomex fire-"
"resistant fabric.  Tough yet breathable, it is light and comfortable to wear"
" under clothing."
msgstr "一件由轻薄诺梅克斯阻燃面料制成的大号紧贴合连体衣。坚韧且透气，轻便舒适，适合穿在衣物内层。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL sleeveless trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "XL sleeveless trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "XL号无袖风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL sleeveless trenchcoat'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive cotton trenchcoat that leaves your arms unencumbered.  Has plenty "
"of storage space due to its many pockets."
msgstr "一件大号棉质风衣，解放你的双臂。因多个口袋而拥有充足的存储空间。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL sleeveless leather trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "XL sleeveless leather trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "XL号无袖皮风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL sleeveless leather trenchcoat'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive leather trenchcoat without sleeves, leaving your arms "
"unencumbered.  Has plenty of storage space due to its many pockets."
msgstr "一件大号无袖皮风衣，解放你的双臂。因多个口袋而拥有充足的存储空间。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "XL trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "XL号风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL trenchcoat'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive cotton trenchcoat, lined with pockets.  Great for storage."
msgstr "一件大号棉质风衣，内衬多个口袋。非常适合存储物品。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "XL leather trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "XL号皮风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather trenchcoat'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive leather trenchcoat, lined with pockets.  Great for storage."
msgstr "一件大号皮风衣，内衬多个口袋。非常适合存储物品。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL duster"
msgid_plural "XL dusters"
msgstr[0] "XL号长款风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL duster'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive full-length duster coat.  Has many pockets for storage."
msgstr "一件大号全长风衣。拥有多个口袋用于存储物品。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather duster"
msgid_plural "XL leather dusters"
msgstr[0] "XL号皮长款风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather duster'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive leather full-length duster.  Has many pockets for storage."
msgstr "一件大号全长皮风衣。拥有多个口袋用于存储物品。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL sleeveless duster"
msgid_plural "XL sleeveless dusters"
msgstr[0] "XL号无袖长款风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL sleeveless duster'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive full-length duster that leaves your arms unencumbered.  Has plenty"
" of storage space due to its many pockets."
msgstr "一件大号全长风衣，解放你的双臂。因多个口袋而拥有充足的存储空间。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL sleeveless leather duster"
msgid_plural "XL sleeveless leather dusters"
msgstr[0] "XL号无袖皮长款风衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL sleeveless leather duster'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive leather full-length duster without sleeves, leaving your arms "
"unencumbered.  Has plenty of storage space due to its many pockets."
msgstr "一件大号无袖全长皮风衣，解放你的双臂。因多个口袋而拥有充足的存储空间。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL cargo pants"
msgid_plural "XL cargo pants"
msgstr[0] "XL号工装裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL cargo pants', 'str_pl': 'XL cargo pants'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of pants lined with pockets, offering lots of storage."
msgstr "一条大号内衬多个口袋的裤子，提供大量存储空间。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL cargo shorts"
msgid_plural "XL cargo shorts"
msgstr[0] "XL号工装短裤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL cargo shorts', 'str_pl': 'XL cargo shorts'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive pair of shorts lined with pockets, offering decent storage."
msgstr "一条大号内衬多个口袋的短裤，提供不错的存储空间。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL plate armor"
msgid_plural "XL plate armors"
msgstr[0] "XL号板甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL plate armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive suit of Gothic plate armor."
msgstr "一套大号哥特式板甲。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL armored gauntlets"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL armored gauntlets"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号装甲护手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL armored gauntlets', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL armored gauntlets'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "An extremely heavy set of massive armor-plated leather gloves."
msgstr "一副极其沉重的巨大装甲皮革手套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL barbute helm"
msgid_plural "XL barbute helms"
msgstr[0] "XL号桶盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL barbute helm'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive medieval helmet that provides excellent protection for the head, "
"with a Y shaped opening for the face."
msgstr "一顶巨大的中世纪头盔，为头部提供极佳保护，面部有Y形开口。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL great helm"
msgid_plural "XL great helms"
msgstr[0] "XL号大盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL great helm'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive medieval helmet that provides excellent protection to the entire "
"head, at the cost of great encumbrance."
msgstr "一顶巨大的中世纪头盔，为整个头部提供极佳保护，但代价是极为笨重。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL O-yoroi"
msgid_plural "XL O-yorois"
msgstr[0] "XL号大铠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL O-yoroi'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A massive ornamental suit of Japanese samurai armor."
msgstr "一套巨大的装饰性日本武士铠甲。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL kabuto"
msgid_plural "XL kabutos"
msgstr[0] "XL号兜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL kabuto'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive medieval Japanese helmet with a scowling facemask that provides "
"excellent protection to the entire head and face."
msgstr "一顶巨大的中世纪日本头盔，配有怒容面甲，为整个头部和面部提供极佳保护。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL faraday plate suit"
msgid_plural "XL faraday plate suits"
msgstr[0] "XL号法拉第板甲套装"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL faraday plate suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive suit of Gothic plate armor, complete with boots, gauntlets, and a "
"barbute helmet.  It has been conductively interconnected, protecting against"
" electricity."
msgstr "一套巨大的哥特式板甲，包括靴子、护手和一顶桶盔。它已导电互连，可抵御电击。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL steel arm guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL steel arm guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号钢制臂甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL steel arm guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL steel arm guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive full assembly of medieval arm protection.  Rerebraces, couters, "
"and vambraces, with leather straps to secure each piece and connect it as "
"part of a set."
msgstr "一套巨大的中世纪手臂防护全组件。包括上臂甲、肘甲和前臂甲，配有皮带以固定每个部件并连接成一套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL cuirass"
msgid_plural "XL cuirasses"
msgstr[0] "XL号胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL cuirass', 'str_pl': 'XL cuirasses'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive steel breastplate, and a vital part of plate armor.  Even as full "
"armor went into decline, cuirasses remained in use among cavalry in Europe."
msgstr "一件巨大的钢制胸甲，是板甲的关键部分。即使全身甲逐渐衰落，胸甲在欧洲骑兵中仍继续使用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL steel leg guards"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL steel leg guards"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号钢制腿甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL steel leg guards', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL steel leg guards'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A masive full assembly of medieval leg protection.  Cuisses, poleyns, and "
"greaves, with leather straps to secure each piece and connect it as part of "
"a set."
msgstr "一套巨大的中世纪腿部防护全组件。包括大腿甲、膝甲和小腿甲，配有皮带以固定每个部件并连接成一套。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL faraday chainmail suit"
msgid_plural "XL faraday chainmail suits"
msgstr[0] "XL号法拉第锁子甲套装"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL faraday chainmail suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive, fully customized chainmail suit.  The coif, shirt, arms, and "
"leggings have been modified with leather straps to deal with uneven weight "
"distribution and to allow them to be used separately.  It has been combined "
"with a set of armored boots and gauntlets and conductively interconnected, "
"protecting against electricity."
msgstr ""
"一套巨大的全定制锁子甲套装。头巾、衬衫、手臂和腿甲已用皮带改装，以应对重量分布不均并允许单独使用。它与一套装甲靴和护手结合，并导电互连，可抵御电击。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chainmail armor"
msgid_plural "XL chainmail armors"
msgstr[0] "XL号锁子甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chainmail armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive fully customized chainmail suit.  The coif, shirt, arms, and "
"leggings have been modified with leather straps to deal with uneven weight "
"distribution and to allow them to be used separately."
msgstr "一套巨大的全定制锁子甲套装。头巾、衬衫、手臂和腿甲已用皮带改装，以应对重量分布不均并允许单独使用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chainmail sleeves"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chainmail sleeves"
msgstr[0] "一副XL号锁子甲袖套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chainmail sleeves', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL chainmail sleeves'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive customized chainmail arms.  Each sleeve has leather straps to "
"connect them with each other.  The lack of fingers makes them less "
"cumbersome and allows them to be used with gloves."
msgstr "巨大的定制锁子甲手臂部件。每个袖套都有皮带相互连接。缺少手指的设计使其不那么笨重，并可与手套搭配使用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chainmail coif"
msgid_plural "XL chainmail coifs"
msgstr[0] "XL号锁子甲头巾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chainmail coif'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive customized chainmail hood.  Can be worn comfortably under helmets."
msgstr "一顶巨大的定制锁子甲头巾。可舒适地戴在头盔下。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chainmail leggings"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chainmail leggings"
msgstr[0] "XL号锁子甲腿套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chainmail leggings', 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL
#. chainmail leggings'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive customized chainmail legs.  Their leather straps keep everything in "
"place, and the lack of toes and heels allows them to work perfectly well "
"with footwear."
msgstr "巨大的定制锁子甲腿部部件。其皮带确保一切固定到位，缺少脚趾和脚跟的设计使其与鞋类完美搭配。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "chainmail vest"
msgid_plural "chainmail vests"
msgstr[0] "锁子甲背心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chainmail vest'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A customized chainmail vest.  It's a sleeveless piece of chainmail with "
"small leather straps designed to better distribute the weight."
msgstr "一件定制的锁子甲背心。这是一件无袖锁子甲，配有小型皮带以更好地分散重量。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL boots"
msgstr[0] "一双XL码靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL boots', 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL
#. boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "Massive leather boots.  Very durable."
msgstr "巨大的皮靴。非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL leather armor boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL leather armor boots"
msgstr[0] "一双XL码皮甲靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL leather armor boots', 'str_pl':
#. 'pairs of XL leather armor boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive leather boots made specifically to protect the feet.  Light and "
"tough."
msgstr "专为保护双脚而制的巨大皮靴。轻便且坚韧。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL armored boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL armored boots"
msgstr[0] "一双XL码装甲靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL armored boots', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. XL armored boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "An extremely heavy set of massive armor plated boots."
msgstr "一套极其沉重的巨大装甲板靴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL chitinous boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL chitinous boots"
msgstr[0] "一双XL码几丁质靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL chitinous boots', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. XL chitinous boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive boots made from the exoskeletons of insects.  Light and durable."
msgstr "由昆虫外骨骼制成的巨大靴子。轻便且耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL biosilicified chitin boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL biosilicified chitin boots"
msgstr[0] "一双XL码生物硅化几丁质靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL biosilicified chitin boots',
#. 'str_pl': 'pairs of XL biosilicified chitin boots'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive boots crafted from carefully cleaned and pruned biosilicified "
"exoskeletons of acidic ants.  Acid-resistant and very durable."
msgstr "由精心清洁和修剪过的酸性蚂蚁生物硅化外骨骼制成的巨大靴子。耐酸且非常耐用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL backpack"
msgid_plural "XL backpacks"
msgstr[0] "XL码背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL backpack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A large backpack.  Good storage for a little encumbrance."
msgstr "一个大背包。提供良好的存储空间，仅带来轻微负担。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL leather backpack"
msgid_plural "XL leather backpacks"
msgstr[0] "XL码皮革背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL leather backpack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "A large leather backpack.  Good storage for a little encumbrance."
msgstr "一个大型皮革背包。提供良好的存储空间，仅带来轻微负担。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL duffel bag"
msgid_plural "XL duffel bags"
msgstr[0] "XL码行李袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL duffel bag'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive duffel bag.  Provides plenty of storage, but is severely "
"encumbering."
msgstr "一个巨大的行李袋。提供充足的存储空间，但会造成严重负担。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL tool belt"
msgid_plural "XL tool belts"
msgstr[0] "XL码工具腰带"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL tool belt'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive belt with pockets and four small belt loops.  Widely used by "
"handymen and electricians if handymen and electricians were bears."
msgstr "一条带有口袋和四个小腰带环的巨大腰带。如果勤杂工和电工是熊的话，他们会广泛使用它。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL chest rig"
msgid_plural "XL chest rigs"
msgstr[0] "XL码胸挂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL chest rig'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive vest covered in webbing, pockets and straps.  This variety is "
"favored by the military, as it is capable of holding four magazines close at"
" hand."
msgstr "一件覆盖着织带、口袋和带子的巨大背心。这种款式深受军方青睐，因为它能容纳四个弹匣，便于取用。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "pair of XL drop leg pouches"
msgid_plural "pairs of XL drop leg pouches"
msgstr[0] "一双XL码腿挂包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of XL drop leg pouches', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of XL drop leg pouches'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A massive set of pouches that can be worn on the thighs using buckled "
"straps.  This variety is favored by the military."
msgstr "一套巨大的包袋，可通过带扣绑带佩戴在大腿上。这种款式深受军方青睐。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL tire armor"
msgid_plural "XL tire armors"
msgstr[0] "XL码轮胎装甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL tire armor'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"Massive makeshift armor made from parts of cut up tires.  Incredibly thick "
"and tough but just as encumbering."
msgstr "由切割轮胎部件制成的巨大临时装甲。极其厚重坚韧，但同样会造成负担。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL hard chest protector"
msgid_plural "XL hard chest protectors"
msgstr[0] "XL码硬质胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL hard chest protector'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A polyurethane chest protector with neoprene backing.  This can be worn "
"regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件带有氯丁橡胶背衬的聚氨酯胸甲。无论你的突变状态如何，都可以穿戴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL conductive suit"
msgid_plural "XL conductive suits"
msgstr[0] "XL码导电服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL conductive suit'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A one piece conductive suit used in linework.  Provides decent physical "
"protection and full protection against electricity.  The hood is designed to"
" fit over a hardhat.  This can be worn regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一件用于线路作业的一体式导电服。提供良好的物理防护和全面的电击防护。兜帽设计用于套在安全帽上。无论你的突变状态如何，都可以穿戴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL floating backpack"
msgid_plural "XL floating backpacks"
msgstr[0] "XL码悬浮背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL floating backpack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A small backpack with a special rail system designed to reduce the load felt"
" by the wearer when moving up and down.  Good storage for very little "
"encumbrance.  This can be worn regardless of your state of mutation"
msgstr "一个小型背包，配有特殊轨道系统，旨在减少穿戴者上下移动时感受到的负荷。提供良好的存储空间，负担极小。无论你的突变状态如何，都可以穿戴。"

#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid "XL floating rucksack"
msgid_plural "XL floating rucksacks"
msgstr[0] "XL悬浮背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'XL floating rucksack'}
#: .\armor_xl.json
msgid ""
"A huge military rucksack with a special rail system designed to reduce the "
"load felt by the wearer when moving up and down, provides a lot of storage "
"for moderate encumbrance.  This can be worn regardless of your state of "
"mutation"
msgstr "一款巨大的军用背包，配有特殊导轨系统，旨在减轻穿戴者上下移动时的负重感，提供大量存储空间且负重适中。无论你的突变状态如何，均可穿戴。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "More Armors"
msgstr "更多护甲"

#. ~ Description for More Armors
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds more armors with recipes. Mainly XL versions for mutated characters, "
"but there are a few new ones too."
msgstr "添加更多带配方的护甲。主要为突变角色设计的XL版本，但也包含一些全新护甲。"
